	<h1 class="title">今日应用：玩了这游戏，你能帮科学家画神经细胞</h1>
	<div class="author-date clearfix">					
			<div class="author clearfix">
					<span class="avatar x25 circle">
						<img src="/system/users/faces/1741/small/1741.jpg?1435203015" alt="">
					</span>
				<span class="name">高宇馨</span>
			</div>
		<span class="date smart-date" data-originDate="2015-05-06 08:27:15 +0800"></span>
	</div>
	<div class="banner">
			<img src="/system/articles/articleshows/9241/medium/9241.jpg?1436687287" alt="" />			
	</div>
	<!-- 传入参数：obj(aritcle, paper, card, mob) -->


